<h3 id="e-mixed-2">Mixed: mobile and desktop</h3>
<p>The grid system has four tiers of classes: xs (extra small), sm (small),
  md (medium), and lg (large). You can use nearly any combination of these classes
  to create more dynamic and flexible layouts.</p>
<p>Each tier of classes scales up, meaning if you plan on setting the same widths for xs and sm,
  you only need to specify xs.</p>
